query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS commission_transactions (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  distributorId INT NOT NULL,
  commissionType ENUM('retail','binary','fast_start','rank_bonus','matching') NOT NULL,
  amount INT NOT NULL,
  sourceOrderId INT,
  sourceDistributorId INT,
  calculationDetails TEXT,
  payoutCycle DATE,
  status ENUM('pending','paid','cancelled') DEFAULT 'pending' NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  paidAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  INDEX idx_distributorId (distributorId),
  INDEX idx_payoutCycle (payoutCycle),
  INDEX idx_status (status)
)
